Flow. for Eating Out

1) Home screen. You choose:
	Eat Out
	Order in
	Cook at home


2) If you select Eat Out, you get three pictures of different restaurants. 

3) Selecting one of the restaurants will give you three choices for meals. Each meal will have a pretty picture, a name, a price and a description. There will also be an add button.
The bottom of the screen will have a 'place order' button, and a 'Order with Notes' button.




